" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 518px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Higher enalapril dose may not be beneficial in HF",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 498px; height: 349px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The NETWORK trial randomized 1532 patients with heart failure to one of three doses of enalapril. After six months of therapy, there was no difference in the primary endpoint (death, heart failure related hospitalization or worsening of heart failure) among the three groups.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
